- content_for :page_title, "Now check your email"
.attention
  %h3= yield :page_title
  %p
    Shortly you should receive an email from PlanningAlerts.org.au. <span class="highlight">Click on the link in the email</span> to
    confirm your comment. Your comment will not be displayed or sent to #{@application.authority.full_name} until you click on the link in the email.
  %p
    If you don't get an email in the next few minutes, try checking your spam filter.
    
